.TH "nvme_submit_admin_passthru" 9 "nvme_submit_admin_passthru" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_submit_admin_passthru \- Submit an nvme passthrough admin command
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nvme_submit_admin_passthru
.BI "(struct nvme_transport_handle *hdl "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hdl" 12
Transport handle
.IP "cmd" 12
The nvme admin command to send
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Uses NVME_IOCTL_ADMIN_CMD for the ioctl request.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, the nvme command status if a response was
received (see \fIenum nvme_status_field\fP) or a negative error otherwise.
